Please recommend 2 to 3 games according to the following requirements. 
You should give your results after "##Output##", but don't include "##Output##" in your answer.
Remember put each game and its description in one line, and do not give any other string except game description.

Here is an example:
##requirements##
Can you recommend me some games on PC platform?
##Output##
The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt is an open-world action role-playing game with a thrilling storyline, engaging characters, and an expansive world to explore, which can be played on PC platform.
Portal 2 is a PC game in first-person puzzle vision that challenges players to solve increasingly complex puzzles using a portal gun.

